    <div class="question">
      <h3>5. Which assumption applies to an ideal gas?</h3>
      <label><input type="radio" name="q5"> a. Molecules strongly attract</label>
      <label><input type="radio" name="q5"> b. Molecules have large volume</label>
      <label><input type="radio" name="q5"> c. No intermolecular forces</label>
