    <div class="question">
      <h3>7. Which substance contains giant covalent bonding?</h3>
      <label><input type="radio" name="q7"> a. CO₂</label>
      <label><input type="radio" name="q7"> b. H₂O</label>
      <label><input type="radio" name="q7"> c. SiO₂</label>
      <label><input type="radio" name="q7"> d. Cl₂</label>
    </div>

    <div class="question">
      <h3>8. Which element is a halogen?</h3>
      <label><input type="radio" name="q8"> a. Na</label>
      <label><input type="radio" name="q8"> b. Mg</label>
