    <div class="question">
      <h3>9. Which oxide is amphoteric?</h3>
      <label><input type="radio" name="q9"> a. Na₂O</label>
      <label><input type="radio" name="q9"> b. MgO</label>
      <label><input type="radio" name="q9"> c. Al₂O₃</label>
      <label><input type="radio" name="q9"> d. SO₃</label>
