    <div class="question">
      <h3>10. 2H₂ + O₂ → 2H₂O. How many moles of water form from 3.0 mol H₂?</h3>
      <label><input type="radio" name="q10"> a. 1.5 mol</label>
      <label><input type="radio" name="q10"> b. 2.0 mol</label>
      <label><input type="radio" name="q10"> c. 3.0 mol</label>
      <label><input type="radio" name="q10"> d. 6.0 mol</label>
    </div>

    <h2>SECTION 2: DATA-BASED / EXPERIMENTAL WORK — 10 marks</h2>

    <div class="question">
