    <h2>SECTION 3: SHORT ANSWER / EXTENDED RESPONSE — 20 marks</h2>

    <div class="question">
      <h3>Question 13 — Sodium chloride [8 marks]</h3>

      <p>(a) Explain why NaCl has high melting point. [2]</p>
